From 072fa08668eac1f38b6cb4d3a21f2a9c8dacdb86 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 17 May 2026 17:31:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix E2E issues across Associations, Communications, and
 Accounting modules
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Associations:
- Add role-aware DashboardHome (PLATFORM_ADMIN sees tenants/settings, TENANT_ADMIN sees associations/accounting/communication)
- Add Users nav link for PLATFORM_ADMIN in sidebar
- Fix board member edit URL trailing space in AssociationBoard.jsx
- Show renter info card in AssociationUnitView when occupancy is RENTED
- Add error prop propagation in AssociationUnitForm for API validation messages
- Fix board member fields not loading in OwnershipAccountEdit (was reading from non-existent unitAssociations array, now reads directly from owner response)

Communications:
- Show status-specific toast in EmailModal: sent/scheduled/draft messages differ
- Replace alert() with toast in RescheduleEmailModal for consistent UX
- Fix SelectRecipientsModal: association checkbox now fetches owners before bulk-selecting them; handleAdd() now shows real owner/vendor names instead of "Owner {id}"
- Improve getRecipientLabel() in TextMessagePage to handle all backend recipient type strings

Accounting:
- Fix General Ledger date filter: rename fromDate→from and toDate→to before sending to backend (LedgerFilter expects 'from'/'to')
- Fix bank account name in Bills pay modal: use bankAccountName field
- Simplify pay bills payload: remove incorrect hard-coded apAccountId/cashAccountId from frontend
- Backend: Make PayBillRequest.apAccountId and cashAccountId optional; BillService auto-detects first LIABILITIES account for AP and first ASSETS account for Cash when not provided
- Fix AddAccountPage error handling to check 'error' field before 'message'
- Hide Confirm Account Number field in AddBankingPage when editing (isEdit mode)
- Add Update Balance button and modal to BankingTab with updateBankBalance API call

